ou hit a =E2=80=9Ctarget=E2=80=9D for your division or the company as a
whole), plus maybe equity, <em>plus</em> a pre-negotiated fee or participat=
ion in the shows or films that you personally oversee. Sometimes you might =
get a higher fee on projects you actually <em>initiate</em>. These are call=
ed =E2=80=9Cshow fees,=E2=80=9D and they serve as a bonus for productivity.=
<br/><br/>Then there are hybrid people, like Feige and Gunn, who <em>make</=
em> movies while also overseeing them as executives. These types will have =
specific talent fees built into their deals. Gunn, for instance,
will earn directing fees, producing fees, and writing fees for his services=
