 guilds would require at least minimum fees. (I=E2=80=99m betting that <str=
ong>Peter Safran</strong>, Gunn=E2=80=99s partner, probably makes a higher =
salary since he handles the bulk of the day-to-day management while Gunn is=
 off making
movies=E2=80=94and earning his individual fees.)<br/><br/>Feige, the vetera=
